This template is for computer busses. You could probably also use it for network hardware systems such as [[Ethernet]], although a separate infobox for networks might be a better idea. For generic hardware components, see [[Template:Infobox Hardware]].

== 用法 ==
<pre>
{{Infobox computer hardware bus
| name        = 匯流排名稱
| fullname-e  = 英文全名
| fullname-c  = 中文全名
| image       = 圖片
| caption     = 圖片註釋
| invent-date = 發明日期
| invent-name = 發明者
| super-name  = 替代介面
| super-date  = 被替代日期
| width       = 匯流排闊度
| numdev      = 最高連接量
| speed       = 頻寬
| style       = 's' for 串行, 'p' for 並行, or plain text
| hotplug     = Does this bus support 熱插拔? (default: 不支持)
| external    = Is this support 外置介面? (default: 不支持)
}}
</pre>
All fields, except 'name' are optional.

See the talk page for some examples which show the full usage of this infobox in a few combinations.

